                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>gāyil: arīd arūḥ ʕa-š-šāyib. anǧaq aš-šāyib yinṭī-ni ǧawāb ʕa-s-suʕālāt hāḏi, qēr-u maḥḥad, maḥḥad ʕid-ne, āni w huwwa w-al-bāše.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
