                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>gāyil-l-u: awwal nōba aʕallm-ak ʕala šnōn ᵊʕrəft-u. al-bāše yōm-in ǧā-niʸ, yōm-in sallam ʕalay-ye lābis yelege, </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
