                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ṣəxme ta-ngūl ᵊngūl ṣəxme yelegit ǧilid, wal, al-yelege ḏīč axēr min-he abad b-al-ᵊblād māmiš. </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
