                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>min hāḏa ʕrəft-u inn-u l-bāše, gilt-ill-u: ahlan wa-sahlan bāšt-i! gāyil: hāḏa timām. gāyil: w-as-sitte? gāyil: ǧīb uxṛa ḏahab!</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
        </ANNOTATION>
        <ANNOTATION>
            <ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a62"
